<h2 class="bold font-l">Elder Bairn Kills Twins </h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Blood-C - Ep 12 (If Remembering Me): Fumito betrays the Organization and siccing a Elder Bairn on them. Two of them, Nono and Nene try to run, with Nono tripping up her sister to save her skin. It's all for naught however. (Edited for censorship in accordance with TVTropes policy.)<br><br> </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PushedAtTheMonster" class='trope-example-link'>Pushed at the Monster</a></p>
